title.rendered: Sentry Cotton Gauze Swabs Non Sterile 10×10 cm, Box of 100

content.rendered:
100% cotton and are french folded to reduce fraying and linting. The gauze swabs are 8ply in thickness and ideal to be used as a secondary wound dressing or absorbing fluid.

Suitable For:

  • Cleaning wounds
  • Sensitive skin
  • Soak up fluid
  • Padding

Product Features:

  • Highly absorbent
